{"word":"G886 - ἀχειροποίητος - acheiropoíētos - akh-i-rop-oy'-ay-tos - Made without hands","slug":"G886","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀχειροποίητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>acheiropoíētos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>akh-i-rop-oy'-ay-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Made without hands"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - acheiropoie&#x0304;tos</b> - <i>akh-i-rop-oy'-ay-tos</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5499\">G5499</a>; <i>unmanufactured</i>, that is, <i>inartificial:</i> - made without (not made with) hands."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5500\">G5500</a>"}]}